    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "You should use the [configure](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/configure.html) widget:\r\n\r\n```js\r\nsearch.addWidget(\r\n  instantsearch.widgets.configure({\r\n    aroundRadius: 1000, // in metric meters\r\n    aroundLatLng: '40.71, -74.01',\r\n  })\r\n);\r\n```\r\n\r\nYou could also use the [searchParameters](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/instantsearch.html#struct-InstantSearchOptions-searchParameters) when instanciating InstantSearch.js.",
