    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "The logic for transforming an address into geo coordinates is done by a geo coder. Algolia provides such a solution and it's called [Algolia Places](https://community.algolia.com/places/). This solution comes with a [widget for InstantSearch.js](https://community.algolia.com/places/examples.html#instantsearchjs).\r\n\r\nIf you want to use another service, you'll have to [make your own integration with a custom widget](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/guides/custom-widget.html).",
    "created_at": "2018-06-04T10:15:06Z",
    "html_url": "https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/2983#issuecomment-394304795",
